          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A demo is a working application that demonstrates a GenAI capability in a form other people can interact with. Unlike a blog post that describes what you built or a code repository that requires setup to run, a demo is immediately accessible. For hiring managers, collaborators, and potential users, a live demo compresses weeks of code reading into 3 minutes of interaction."
          }
        ]
      },
