        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "What Demos Demonstrate (Beyond the Obvious)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A demo is not just a proof that a technique works. To an experienced evaluator, a well-constructed demo reveals:"
