                    "text": "{'type': 'text', 'text': 'Honest evaluation.', 'marks': [{'type': 'bold'}]} {'type': 'text', 'text': ' A demo that shows failures alongside successes, or that surfaces confidence or uncertainty in outputs, signals intellectual honesty that impresses more than a polished demo that only shows the cases where the model is correct.'}"
