            "type": "text",
            "text": "A demo converts GenAI skills from a claim into evidence. The highest-impact demos solve a specific real problem, document failure modes alongside capabilities, and reveal architecture judgment through their structure. Hugging Face Spaces is the primary distribution platform for ML demos. Secrets and cost controls are operational prerequisites for any public demo, not optional polish. Three curated, well-documented demos that honestly show tradeoffs are more valuable than ten experiments that only demonstrate the technique worked once."
